# Version control
.git
.gitignore

# Go workspace files — untracked and developer-local. Leaving them in
# the build context puts the image in workspace mode (resolves modules
# via go.work.sum), which can trip the pre-split/split genproto
# ambiguity. CI never has go.work, so excluding matches CI behaviour.
go.work
go.work.sum

# Local state and logs
state/
logs/

# Test artifacts
*_test.go
tests/

# Dashboard source (built separately)
dashboard/

# Docs
docs/
*.md
*.docx
*.txt

# OS artifacts
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/